OL,6,FActor Hugh Grant spoke to ITV News
OL,7,FCorrespondent Rebecca Barry about the
OL,8,Ftabloid he believes commissioned
OL,9,Funlawful invasions of his privacy
OL,11,FHugh Grant has told ITV News he
OL,12,Fremains "bitter and determined to
OL,13,Fexact justice" on those in the
OL,14,Fnewspaper industry he believes
OL,15,Fcommissioned unlawful activity to
OL,16,Finvade his privacy.
OL,18,FAppearing in a new ITV documentary -
OL,19,FTabloids On Trial - the actor speaks
OL,20,Ffor the first time about his recent
OL,21,Fsettlement with The Sun newspaper.
