OL,6,FPrince Harry, Charlotte Church, Paul
OL,7,FGascoigne and Gordon Brown also
OL,8,Ffeature in the programme which airs on
OL,9,FITV1 and ITVX at 9pm on Thursday.
OL,11,FI've been reporting on the phone
OL,12,Fhacking scandal for more than a
OL,13,Fdecade, but Grant tells me "this isn't
OL,14,Fonly about phone hacking."
OL,16,F"There were microphones in window
OL,17,Fboxes outside the house. There were
OL,18,Ftrackers, microphones dropped into my
OL,19,Fcar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
