OL,6,F"There were medical records of me, the
OL,7,Fmothers of my children and ex-
OL,8,Fgirlfriends - all blagged and stolen
OL,9,Fout of the NHS. And perhaps most
OL,10,Fspectacularly the burglary of both my
OL,11,Fflat and my office."
OL,13,FHe made these claims in his recent
OL,14,FHigh Court civil case against News
OL,15,FGroup Newspapers (NGN), the publisher
OL,16,Fof The Sun. NGN has always strongly
OL,17,Fdenied the allegations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
