OL,6,F"In the case of my flat burglary, it
OL,7,Fwas quite spectacular," Grant
OL,8,Fexplained, "the whole door had been
OL,9,Ftaken off its hinges, they'd been
OL,10,Fthrough the flat and nothing was
OL,11,Fstolen."
OL,13,F"They'd been there to get information
OL,14,Fand a lot of information about the
OL,15,Finterior and the contents of my flat
OL,16,Fappeared in newspapers a couple of
OL,17,Fdays later."
