OL,6,FThe actor and campaigner said he
OL,7,Freluctantly settled out-of-court with
OL,8,FNews Group Newspapers for "an enormous
OL,9,Fsum" of money, because civil
OL,10,Flitigation rules mean even if he had
OL,11,Fwon at trial he could have faced a #10
OL,12,Fmillion bill.
OL,14,FThe publisher of The Sun settled
OL,15,Fwithout any admission of liability.
OL,17,F"If you're innocent, why do you shove
OL,18,Fso much money at someone not to go to
OL,19,Fcourt?" asks Grant.
