OL,6,FIt has been almost two decades since
OL,7,Fthe phone hacking scandal broke, but
OL,8,Fdespite apologies and more than #1
OL,9,Fbillion spent on legal fees and pay-
OL,10,Fouts by two of Britain's biggest
OL,11,Fnewspaper groups - for many victims
OL,12,Fthe pain endures.
OL,14,FFor Charlotte Church, it began when
OL,15,Fshe was a teenager.J"From the ages of
OL,16,F15 to 21, I had an inescapable abuser:
OL,17,Fthe press," Church said.
OL,19,FAt 16-years-old the singer was being
OL,20,Fhacked by the News of the World.
