OL,6,FShe described her "paranoia and
OL,7,Fanxiety" as she and her family would
OL,8,Fwonder "have they got microphones in
OL,9,Four house?"
OL,11,FChurch said her mother was preyed upon
OL,12,Feven as she experienced a mental
OL,13,Fhealth crisis.
OL,15,F"My mother was already an incredibly
OL,16,Fvulnerable woman. Her mental health
OL,17,Fwas really bad. And I'd found her
OL,18,Fafter taking an overdose, and so she
OL,19,Fwas in a really bad way and that was
OL,20,Fstraight in the press.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
