OL,6,F"It was horrific. She's never been
OL,7,Fable to fully come back from the abuse
OL,8,Fthat she suffered."
OL,10,FIn 2012, News Group Newspapers - the
OL,11,Fpublisher of the now defunct News of
OL,12,Fthe World -paid substantial damages to
OL,13,FChurch and her family and offered its
OL,14,F"sincere apologies".
OL,16,FBut back in the early 2000s even
OL,17,Fnational heroes became victims.
