OL,6,FPaul Gascoigne is widely regarded as
OL,7,Fone of the best footballers England
OL,8,Fhas ever produced, but in an emotional
OL,9,Finterview he said phone hacking made
OL,10,Fhim so paranoid he became a "recluse,"
OL,11,Ftoo scared to speak to anyone.
OL,13,FThe former footballer broke down in
OL,14,Ftears as he told me he even suspected
OL,15,Fhis own parents of selling stories to
OL,16,Fthe papers.
