OL,6,F"I was just speaking to my mum and
OL,7,Fdad, just them - and the next day it
OL,8,Fcame out in the papers. So I went mad.
OL,9,FI said, what the f*** are you speaking
OL,10,Fto the papers for?
OL,12,F"They said I haven't spoken to them. I
OL,13,Fsaid, you have. You're the only two
OL,14,FI've spoken to. I love my mum and dad,
OL,15,Fso the thought they were hacking us
OL,16,Fwasn't good."
OL,18,FGascoigne sued Mirror Group Newspapers
OL,19,F(MGN) - who in 2015 were ordered to
OL,20,Fpay damages, publicly admitted the
OL,21,Fwrongdoing and apologised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
