OL,7,Fwas settled with a full apology in
OL,8,F2012, and a later claim in 2021
OL,9,Fagainst The Sun was settled without
OL,10,Fadmission of liability.
OL,12,FOther allegations reach the very heart
OL,13,Fof power.
